<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	xmlns:h="http://java.sun.com/jsf/html"
	xmlns:f="http://java.sun.com/jsf/core">



<h:head>

	<title>Presentazione Palestra</title>
	<link href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"></link>

	<script
		src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.2/jquery.min.js"></script>

	<script src="bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</h:head>


<h:body>

	<div class="container">
		<div class="row"  style="padding-top:10px">
		<img src="img/banner.jpg" />
		
		</div >
		
		<div class="row"  style="padding-top:10px">
		<div class="col-md-10">
		<h3>Benvenuti nella palestra Gruppi Fitness TIMETABLE</h3>
		<h5>La nostra palestra offre svariati tipi di corsi per tutte le esigenze.<br />Il nostro scopo Ã¨ dare il benessere ai nostri clienti.<br />
		Di seguito le tipologie di corsi offerti da noi..</h5>
		</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row" style="padding-top:10px">
			<div class="col-md-10">
			<h:form>
				<h:dataTable value="#{tc.tipoCorsi}" var="t">

					<h:column>
						<f:facet name="header">Nome</f:facet>
       					<h:commandLink value="#{t.nome}" action="#{tc.recuperaCorsi(t.nome)}" />
     				</h:column>
					
					<h:column>
						<f:facet name="header">Descrizione</f:facet>
						 #{t.descrizione}
							
					</h:column>
				</h:dataTable>
			</h:form>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</h:body>
</html>